{
    "zh-CN": {
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_NAME": "纵火者",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "纵火者是一名短程坦克，以火为手段达到目的。管理他的过热计量表使他能够对敌群造成大量伤害。平衡是胜利的关键。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SUBTITLE": "疯狂纵火狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_NORMAL_GAUGE_NAME": "普通计量表",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_NORMAL_GAUGE_DESCRIPTION": "对白色部分造成<style=cIsDamage>100%</style>伤害。基础计量表对过热有抗性。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_NAME": "暴击计量表",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_DESCRIPTION": "对白色部分造成<style=cIsDamage>70%</style>伤害，对蓝色部分造成<style=cIsDamage>250%</style>伤害。最大热量固定。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_NAME": "Dragon's Breath",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_DESCRIPTION": "发射一道火焰光束，造成<style=cIsDamage>90%伤害</style>。离目标越近，点燃几率越高。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_NAME": "Fireball",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热量。</style>发射一枚火球，命中时造成<style=cIsDamage>225%伤害并点燃</style>敌人。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ALT_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_NAME": "Overdrive",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ALT_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热量。</style><style=cIsUtility>超级暴击。</style>发射一枚火球，命中时造成<style=cIsDamage>160%伤害并点燃</style>敌人。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_SCEPTER_NAME": "Firestorm",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热量。</style>发射一道灼热穿透光束，命中时造成<style=cIsDamage>300%伤害并点燃</style>敌人。短暂蓄力后，松开时发射一道毁灭性光束造成<style=cIsDamage>450%伤害</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_NAME": "Zero Point Blast",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热量。</style>向前推进，引爆身后敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。发射后立即撞击第一个敌人会在周围引发爆炸造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_NAME": "信号枪",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_DESCRIPTION": "发射一枚信号弹，在5秒内造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>，然后爆炸造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>，释放5枚信号弹各造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_UTILITY_CLEANSE_NAME": "净化",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_UTILITY_CLEANSE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热量。</style><style=cIsDamage>点燃</style>周围区域，对附近敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>50%</style>伤害并移除其他状态效果。提供少量速度提升。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_NAME": "Masochism",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热量。</style>被<style=cIsDamage>点燃</style>造成的伤害转化为<style=cIsHealing>治疗</style>，持续6.5秒。增加<style=cIsDamage>125%</style>攻击速度。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_NAME": "受虐狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_DESCRIPTION": "当达到<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>上限时，周期性地对自己造成伤害，以换取范围<style=cIsHealing>生命偷取</style>和灼烧。最多10秒后，<style=cIsDamage>引爆</style>，然后<style=cIsUtility>过热</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_NAME": "怨恨",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_DESCRIPTION": "当达到<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>上限时，你移动更快并获得<style=cKeywordName>双重射击</style>和<style=cIsHealing>生命偷取</style>。最多10秒后，<style=cIsDamage>引爆</style>，然后<style=cIsUtility>过热</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_NAME": "Dante's Rebuke",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "发射一道强烈光束，造成<style=cIsDamage>140%伤害</style>。离目标越近，点燃几率越高。按住2秒或更久后，松开时发射一道最终光束，造成<style=cIsDamage>150%伤害</style>。Original mod by PopcornFactory</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_ANTICIPATION": "<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>每失去和/或获得100热量，纵火者获得1层预判；获得5层后，他可激活受虐狂；额外层数增加伤害和持续时间；所有层数在结束时消耗。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_DETONATE": "<style=cKeywordName>引爆</style>纵火者爆炸，造成<style=cIsDamage>150%伤害</style>乘以累积的预判层数。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在受虐狂激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>18%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_SURGE_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在怨恨激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>5%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_OVERHEAT_MASO": "<style=cKeywordName>过热：受虐狂</style>如果纵火者因热量积累过多而退出受虐狂，则应用EX过热，将其移动速度和伤害降低至70%。取消或让技能自然结束会应用过热，将其攻击速度降低至50%。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_TEXT": "过热！",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_COOLING_TEXT": "冷却中...！",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_EX_TEXT": "过热：EX！"
    }
}
